              What we offer
            </span>
            <h2 class="font-aktiv text-kd-gold text-[28px] md:text-[36px] font-semibold leading-[36px] md:leading-[48px] tracking-[1.4px] md:tracking-[1.8px] mb-4">
              Signature services
            </h2>
            <p class="font-montserrat text-kd-grey text-[15px] md:text-[16px] font-light leading-[24px] md:leading-[28px] tracking-[1.5px] md:tracking-[1.6px]">
